{"componentChunkName":"component---src-template-page-bs-js","path":"/libraries/chess-library/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<p>In 2017, I began an adult chess library program for <a href=\"http://www.cvlga.org/\">Chattahoochee Valley Libraries</a> in Columbus, Georgia. It’s been a hit with our community and continues to grow. I believe that its success comes from the way chess transcends the gaps between diverse people.</p>\n<p>In 2019, we hosted our first open tournament.</p>\n<p>I wasn’t satisfied with any of of the existing rule handouts I could find, so I wrote my own. <a href=\"/libraries/how-play-chess/\">You can read the online version of the handout here</a>. Feel free to copy and adapt it for your own programs.</p>","frontmatter":{"date":"August 15, 2018","isoDate":"2018-08-15T00:00:00.000Z","title":"Chess at the Library: my public library chess program","description":"Placeholder.","thumbnail":{"caption":"A chessboard at the library.","image":{"publicURL":"/static/ce146bc0887c95d55f82996010886ac0/Chess.jpg","sharpImg":{"mobileImage":{"srcSet":"/static/ce146bc0887c95d55f82996010886ac0/aabdf/Chess.jpg 150w,\n/static/ce146bc0887c95d55f82996010886ac0/9dc27/Chess.jpg 300w,\n/static/ce146bc0887c95d55f82996010886ac0/4fe8c/Chess.jpg 600w,\n/static/ce146bc0887c95d55f82996010886ac0/9842e/Chess.jpg 900w,\n/static/ce146bc0887c95d55f82996010886ac0/47498/Chess.jpg 1200w,\n/static/ce146bc0887c95d55f82996010886ac0/ec6c5/Chess.jpg 1280w","src":"/static/ce146bc0887c95d55f82996010886ac0/4fe8c/Chess.jpg","sizes":"(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px","aspectRatio":1.3274336283185841},"tabletImage":{"srcSet":"/static/ce146bc0887c95d55f82996010886ac0/9dc27/Chess.jpg 300w,\n/static/ce146bc0887c95d55f82996010886ac0/4fe8c/Chess.jpg 600w,\n/static/ce146bc0887c95d55f82996010886ac0/47498/Chess.jpg 1200w,\n/static/ce146bc0887c95d55f82996010886ac0/ec6c5/Chess.jpg 1280w","src":"/static/ce146bc0887c95d55f82996010886ac0/47498/Chess.jpg","sizes":"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px